Name: Bullseye
About the game: What better way to kill time than shooting arrows at a target in the middle of the ocean? Bullseye has two game modes: Relaxed and Parkour. Relaxed: Take a break and relax by shooting arrows in the middle of the calm ocean. Parkour: Jump off walls and shoot in mid-air to compete on the Steam Leaderboards for the fastest bullseye! 10 Relaxed levels, 20 Parkour levels. Average play-through time is 1-2 hours, varying based on how good your aim is, and how many achievements and high scores you want.
